C

Config - Annotation Type in configurator.annotations
The simplest version, injects properties from the environmental variables, system properties, or property files as a String.
ConfigJson - Annotation Type in configurator.annotations
Injects JSON from the environmental variables, system properties, property files, JSON files, URLs, and class members.
ConfigTyped - Annotation Type in configurator.annotations
A convenience version, injects properties from the environmental variables, system properties, or property files and automatically tries to parse loaded String values to the Java data types: Double, Float, Long, Integer, Short, Byte, Character, Boolean.
configurator - package configurator
 
configurator.annotations - package configurator.annotations
 
ConfiguratorSetup - Annotation Type in configurator.annotations
The @ConfiguratorSetup annotation is used to configure paths and settings of the Configurator.

getDefaultValue() - Method in class configurator.TypedProperty

getPropertyName() - Method in class configurator.TypedProperty
Depending on the attribute used, returns a property name for properties, a file path for files, a URL address for URLs, and a field or method name for class members.
getValue() - Method in class configurator.TypedProperty
Returns injected value (or null if any error).
getValueOr(T) - Method in class configurator.TypedProperty

getValueOrDefaultValue() - Method in class configurator.TypedProperty

getValueOrDefaultValueOr(T) - Method in class configurator.TypedProperty
